      "content": "wait sorry, what did you mean by the goblin thing? i'm not sure how that relates to frequency ratios at all. can you just stick to the acoustics part? also, you mentioned something about the difference being \"large\"—isn't a minor second actually a very small interval? i'm a bit confused about the math there.",
